description.1: Chaos erupts in Manhattan as Xandu attempts to merge the world of the dead with the world of the living! While Doctor Strange, Scarlet Witch, and Spider-Man battle the warlock in the underworld, can Cap stand alone against an army of undead?
description.5: Will Richard Rider, AKA Nova, finally see sparks fly with Namorita?
description.10: After Sabretooth's betrayed, he'll stop at nothing for revenge. Victor Creed continues to face his painful past along the way. Will he be able to stay focused on his goal?
description.11: Who murdered Lisa Beckman? Daimon Hellstrom knows, and he's dying to spill secrets.
description.13: He has slashed his way through many battles and fears nothing. But what will Wolverine do when he must confront a terrifying truth? The Truth about… Killing.
description.21: An Infinity Crusade crossover! The return of Hawkeye as Clint Barton goes back to his heroic roots!
description.25: Dark forces are brewing in the streets of New York, and they're going to change Matt Murdock's life forever! An all-star cast of characters- Silver Sable, Ben Urich, The Hand, and more- all begin to converge, starting with a single question- who or what is the Snakeroot?
description.26: The battle rages on in Loch Ness, Scotland between the Hulk, Piecemeal and Madman! And Perseus gets caught in the crosshairs!
description.27: The Goddess still has her sights set on the billion dollar playboy! But after a deadly battle against the Technovore, Tony Stark is given a second chance to serve the Goddess. Will he abandon Earth and accept her offer?
description.29: Miguel O' Hara is the half-Irish, half-Mexican engineer who has donned the mask of Spider-Man. But how well do we really know the man behind the mask? A shocking and revelatory issue!
description.30: Zeus reaches a conclusion regarding Thor, while the Thunder God does unholy battle against the Super Skrull in the name of the Goddess.
description.32: Lila Cheney is BACK and is taking Guido on a wild trip to the other side of the universe! Forge steps into a new role at Val Cooper's behest, and Alex and Rahne pay a difficult visit to Xavier's following the death of Magik.
description.35: Professor X has yet another mission for Wolverine and Jubilee! The duo search the former headquarters of cybernetic mutant-hunters the Reavers, but little do they know… someone's home. And this someone is out for Jubilee.
description.44: Galen Kor, leader of the Kree army, makes his opening move in a quest for vengeance! The Avengers are outnumbered, and may well be overpowered in battle!
description.46: D-Man held captive by the Night People! Will Cap be able to save Demolition-Man's life? Find out as Captain America and D-Man take on impossible odds in Captain America #418!
description.48: Soulfire and Hellstorm-enemies no longer! Uniting against a common foe, the Son of Satan and a spawn of Satan do unholy battle in the ""Damnation Game.""
description.52: The Hand wants Sabretooth's head! With no back-up to speak of, Sabretooth must face an excruciating fight, both physically and mentally.
description.55: The Poison Memories are going down—Rage is going to make sure of it!
description.61: The rage of ROADKILL! The wrathful spirit is out for revenge, and he'll get it even if that means going straight through Namorita! But he'll also have to face off with another man who knows a thing or two about revenge, as the Punisher comes bearing down on Roadkill's rampage!
description.63: An Infinity Crusade crossover! When the Goddess turns half of the heroes to her crusade, it means Avengers West Coast members vs Avengers West Coast members!
description.74: A gaggle of Super Villains may be too much for the Man Without Fear to handle alone!
description.75: Hulk is shocked to find Piecemeal at the Lake of Loch Ness, instead of its fabled resident monster!
description.76: When Iron Man encounters techno organic creatures, on a quest to consume all matter, he must use his arsenals of armored suits to combat the Technovore!
description.78: Miguel may have a strained relationship with his mother Conchata, and a tenuous relationship with his brother Gabe, but family is family. When Spider-Man falls into toxic trouble with Alchemax, the O'Hara family comes together to solve the missing pieces...and save Miguel's life.
description.79: Thor is introduced to the rest of the Goddess' heroes. The Goddess spins a deceptive spell over her newest follower.
description.82: The FF's battle with the Fearsome Foursome crashes headlong into the trial of Johnny Storm! But even though Johnny's not allowed to flame on, have no fear: Daredevil, Spider-Man, and the Avengers arrive to help out! It's a Marvel-wide melee for the ages!
description.83: Wolverine and Rogue must work together to fight their way through the Savage Land! Can they escape a horde of dinosaurs and find Sauron in time?
description.92: Hellstorm is nearly grounded at the airport when the demonic Soulfire unleashes hell from… well, Hell.
description.96: Kree Sentries attack the Avengers and find an unlikely ally in Deathcry, a Shi'Ar warrior. But is this just the beginning of Kree retribution against the Avengers?
description.98: Captain America: Terminated! Witness the epic conclusion to Cap and Kazar's battle against A.I.M. in the Savage Lands!

0.text: Talon reveals his origins to his teammates!

1.text: Chaos erupts in Manhattan as Xandu attempts to merge the world of the dead with the world of the living! While Doctor Strange, Scarlet Witch, and Spider-Man battle the warlock in the underworld, can Cap stand alone against an army of undead?

2.text: Out of the frying pan... just as Han Solo and Chewbacca manage to escape the wiles of Mystra and the arena of Raskar with the last of the legendary power gems, Luke and Threepio turn up missing. They've in fact crash-landed on the ice planet Hoth, where they're rescued by a mysterious benefactor who has decidedly different plans for the pair than her father: a father who wants to off Luke and dismantle the loyal droid for scrap!

3.text: Punisher and Venom come face-to-face! Talk about an unpredictable duo…!

4.text: Return of the SINISTER SYNDICATE! A band of Spidey's nemeses join together once more to take the Web-Head down -- but they've got more firepower this time out! One of Spider-Man's greatest foes enters the fray -- DOCTOR OCTOPUS!

6.text: It's Hammer Brothers Time! Hammers clash when Mjolnir-wielder of the future Dargo Ktor is tricked into fighting Eric Masterson, the replacement Thor, in the modern day. As they bring the thunder, Beta Ray Bill joins the party with his mighty mallet Stormbreaker!

7.text: Chthon, patron demon of the Darkhold, receives an appeal from Modred for the return of his soul. But will the Elder God listen?

8.text: John Walker discovers the truth behind the Scourge organization. Later, he runs into Bloodstain and their shocking, connected history is revealed!

9.text: It’s a full-on brawl against Darkhawk and Night Thrasher amidst the heroes, Havok, Human Torch, Spider-Woman, Mr. Fantastic, Vision, Cyclops, and more!

12.text: Angel comes to the X-Men with a message, but can he be trusted?

14.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 11 Spider-Man and his teammates must contend with Shriek while Venom is tortured by Carnage!

15.text: Adam Warlock must search for answers within while he does battle with his greatest enemy...himself!
Adam Warlock must search for answers within while he does battle with his greatest enemy...himself!

17.text: Deadpool must make his way through a battalion of mercenaries in Sarajevo, Yugoslavia. Little does he know that Weapon X is lying in wait to take him down!
Deadpool must make his way through a battalion of mercenaries in Sarajevo, Yugoslavia. Little does he know that Weapon X is lying in wait to take him down!

18.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 12 After clearing the streets of wild and enraged denizens of New York City, Spider-Man and his team are ready for an epic showdown with Carnage and his cronies!

20.text: Sinister reveals the truth about the Legacy Virus!

21.text: An Infinity Crusade crossover! The return of Hawkeye as Clint Barton goes back to his heroic roots!

31.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 10 Cloak, Morbius, and Black Cat face off against Carrion, Demogoblin, and Doppelganger!

34.text: Ms. Marvel uncontrollably mutates into an even more grotesque version of She-Thing!

38.text: FATAL ATTRACTIONS, PART 2 X-Force's HQ is invaded by an unwelcome guest, a man who is taking the team out member by member. Magneto makes a play for certain X-Force members...and succeeds!

42.text: Wong channels Strange’s astral from to battle Baron Blood II!

45.text: It's Cable versus G.W. Bridge! Plus, what will a newly-reunited Six Pack decide to do with Cable?
It's Cable versus G.W. Bridge! Plus, what will a newly-reunited Six Pack decide to do with Cable?

47.text: In this Infinity Crusade crossover, a luminous entity emerges from depths of the sea. Darkhawk exchanges blows with this new enemy merely to find that they are made up of pure evil.

49.text: Learn the “Family Ties” of Night Thrasher, AKA Dwayne Taylor, in his solo series debut!

50.text: Experience what it’s like to roam through the Xavier’s School for Gifted Youngsters! A complete guide on what and where everything is---from the living quarters to the Danger Room!

51.text: Rogue is in search for a cure for her mutant powers, but is it too good to be true?

53.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 14 It's the conclusion of one of Spider-Man's biggest events ever.  It all comes down to this: Spider-Man vs. Venom vs. Carnage.  Can Spidey stop the chaos before New York is changed forever?

54.text: Venom has made a peaceful truce…with Spider-Man?!

56.text: Ghost Rider and the Midnight Sons must take down one of their own…a demonically possessed Blade!

57.text: With his cover blown, U.S. Agent must escape the Scourge organization and put a halt to their path of destruction.

58.text: The Guardians must obtain the mystical Book of Kells due to its ability to create a new beginning for Earth's citizens. The only thing in their way? Cuchulain the Irish Wolfhound and Shamrock! One can assume the luck of the Irish will be working against the Guardians!

59.text: The battle between Rancor and Doctor Doom rages on! Meanwhile, Major Victory sacrifices something near and dear to him.

60.text: Details of Luke’s personal life are now public domain! Crusader comes in for the kill.

61.text: The rage of ROADKILL! The wrathful spirit is out for revenge, and he'll get it even if that means going straight through Namorita! But he'll also have to face off with another man who knows a thing or two about revenge, as the Punisher comes bearing down on Roadkill's rampage!

62.text: The Finale! The Invaders take on the combined forces of Battle-Axis, the Golem, and Vision!

63.text: An Infinity Crusade crossover! When the Goddess turns half of the heroes to her crusade, it means Avengers West Coast members vs Avengers West Coast members!

65.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 8 Spider-Man, Venom, Black Cat, Cloak, and Firestar enlist J. Jonah Jameson in their war against Carnage!

66.text:
FATAL ATTRACTIONS, PART 1
What is the truth behind Project Wideawake? X-Factor, Acolytes and the return of a mutant menace!

68.text: The true origins of the two Psylockes revealed!

69.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 7 Spider-Man, along with Venom, Cloak, and Black Cat head to a place from Cletus Kasady's past to search for clues as to where Carnage might be.

70.text: The Fantastic Four, the Avengers, the Defenders, the X-Men, X-Factor, X-Force, the New Warriors and more are turned against each other in the Goddess' cosmic inquisition!
The Fantastic Four, the Avengers, the Defenders, the X-Men, X-Factor, X-Force, the New Warriors and more are turned against each other in the Goddess' cosmic inquisition!

73.text: Excalibur helps the last heroes of 2015 defeat R.C.X. of the present!

80.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 6 Venom, Cloak and Black Cat set out to locate Morbius and have him join up in the fight against Carnage!

85.text: Can Silver Surfer and his team defeat Tyrant?

89.text: The Golem joins forces with the Golden Age Vision against the Invaders.

90.text: Spider-Man 2099 must combat a murderer with a dangerous obsession for evolution. And this villain will do anything to adapt and conquer! (Note: this issue does not contain the Hulk 2099 story in the original print version.)

91.text: In this issue Luke Skywalker encounters a menacing Darth Vader at the Iron Tower on Aridus, and a new friend posing as an old one gives his life to save Luke and the natives of Aridus from Vader's treachery. Meanwhile, a Rebel scheme for destroying Vader's private cruiser unfolds, with the legendary power gems of the Pirates of Iridium holding the key. Han Solo and Chewbacca volunteer to retrieve the gem, but don't count on being thrown to the wolves in the bargain!

94.text: When Black Widow disappears following the trail of a psychic and sadastic killer, Daredevil will have to find his partner before the killer strikes again.

97.text: THE HOT NEW SPIDER-MAN ONGOING CONTINUES!SPIDER-MAN and RED-HULK lead an underground army in this action packed extravaganza from superstar artist JOE MADUREIRA
Cable has made it back to his Swiss Alps residence in the present but Bridge is still hunting him and he's getting closer by the minute. Meanwhile, a group of mercenaries are searching for Deadpool.

99.text: Rusty and Skids are taken hostage by the Friends of Humanity to "pay for their mutant crimes"! Will the rest of the team offer a timely assist?
